    <item>
      <title>Products</title>
      <link>http://tigoctm.com/products/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Nov 2015 23:11:06 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://tigoctm.com/products/</guid>
      <description>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;http://lamassu.is&#34;&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://i.imgur.com/zOIjbbg.png&#34; alt=&#34;Lamassu Bitcoin Ventures&#34; /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
Tigo CTM uses &lt;a href=&#34;http://lamassu.is&#34;&gt;Lamassu&lt;/a&gt; machines because they are the most popular in the industry, and they have a free and open software stack.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For each level, Tigo operators also get &lt;a href=&#34;http://dash.org&#34;&gt;Dash&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://deginner.com/ctm&#34;&gt;cosigning&lt;/a&gt;, and other value add features pre-installed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;douro:00bfec932a1288b5fcd69397805e20e9&#34;&gt;Douro&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://lamassu.is/content/uploads/douro-product-overview.jpg?5bc813&#34; align=&#34;center&#34; class=&#34;responsive-img&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lamassu&amp;rsquo;s basic model, the Douro, lets users buy Bitcoin with cash. This one-directional operation is the simplest place to start, and may have legal advantages in some jurisdictions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h4 id=&#34;braga:00bfec932a1288b5fcd69397805e20e9&#34;&gt;Braga&lt;/h4&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://lamassu.is/content/uploads/braga-product-overview-focussed.png&#34; align=&#34;center&#34; class=&#34;responsive-img&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This floor stand is designed to match the Douro, and cuts down installation work by 90%. Tigo can help with custom installations, for those who desire.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;h2 id=&#34;santa-tirso:00bfec932a1288b5fcd69397805e20e9&#34;&gt;Santa Tirso&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://lamassu.is/content/uploads/santo-tirso-product-overview-focussed.png&#34; align=&#34;center&#34; class=&#34;responsive-img&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Lamassu&amp;rsquo;s two-way upgrade Santa Tirso, lets users buy &lt;strong&gt;and sell&lt;/strong&gt; Bitcoin with cash. It also doubles as a stand, replacing the Braga.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
